window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>\"The greatest story ever told\" is more than just a cliché.</b></p> <p>God goes to great lengths to rescue lost and hurting people, and that is what <i>The Story</i> is all about: the story of the Bible, God’s great love affair with humanity. Filled with intrigue, drama, conflict, and redemption, this dramatized edition sweeps you into the stories, poems, and teachings of the Bible.</p> <p>Features:<br> &nbsp;</p> <p></p> <ul> <li>Multiple voices, professional narration, music, and sound effects bring this dramatic recording to life</li> <li>Audio foreword from Max Lucado</li> <li>New International Version (NIV) Bible text, with short transitions to connect the listener to the continuing story</li> </ul>"; 
